{"tid":1589772,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"教下大家一個維修小知識 蜜糖好易整懷機器","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:11:56.000Z","uid":163492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da18cd84eb9fd625bd8d46ea245ac133092f6e41","tid":1589772,"uid":163492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"有個師傅 佢做維修<br />\n試過同公司嘈交<br />\n遲職前 唔小心張<br />\n蜜糖用當錯係潤滑油<br />\n跟住幾個月後部機壞左<br />\n<br />\n佢話聽老師傅講<br />\n機器用左蜜糖會越搞越杰<br />\n最後整壞部機<br />\n所以大家要少心<br />\n唔好張蜜糖當錯雪油<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法缺點<br />\n部機可能要幾個月先壞<br />\n但係清潔起黎都煩"},{"pid":"33777cd313a372e20858476aecab2847b695c203","tid":1589772,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"9190168ffd0b256e7f6fac5812ecee3ecc1ff23f","tid":1589772,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:11:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>十一國殤 全民黑衣</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ishNdyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FishNdyx.jpg&h=21d2a745&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTDkyyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTDkyyx.jpg&h=565c80c5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}